Package ca.corefacility.gview.map.gui.editor.panel.propertyMapper

Provides classes for the Property Mapper panel.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    COGToColorMapperListItem
    This class represents a single COG category to color as a list item.
    COGToColorPanel
    The COG to color panel.
    ContinuousMapperListItem
    This class represents a continuous property style mapper list item.
    DiscreteMapperListItem
    This class represents a discrete property style mapper list item.
    PropertyMapperChooserDialog
    A subclass of JDialog, used for returning a new PropertyMapperListItem.
    PropertyMapperList
    This class is a customization of JList that is intended to contain only property mapper list items and render them appropriately.
    PropertyMapperListItem
    This class represents a generic property style mapper list item.
    PropertyMapperPanel
    The property style mapper panel.
